<HL>
   Agency Rules
   Cement Imports
   Hurt U.S. Firms
   ----
   By Eduardo Lachica
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/14/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A9
</SO>
